# 5ï¸âƒ£ SUPER LIFEHACKLAR â€” DARSNING ENG QIZIQ JOYI

## â­ 1. `mkdir` + `cd` ni birga qilish

```bash
mkdir newproj && cd newproj
```

## â­ 2. `touch` bilan â€œproject templateâ€ yaratish

```bash
touch {index.html,app.js,style.css,README.md}
```

## â­ 3. Tasodifiy fayl yaratish (test uchun)

```bash
touch test_$(date +%s).txt
```

## â­ 4. Fayllarni oâ€˜chirishdan oldin koâ€˜rish (dry-run)

```bash
ls | grep ".log"
```

## â­ 5. `rm` xavfsiz alternative â€” alias yasash

```bash
alias rm='rm -i'
```

Har safar tasdiq soâ€˜raydi.

